def "tale:china_butterfly_dream" "Zhuangzi dreams he is a butterfly, drifting and content, knowing nothing of Zhuangzi; waking, he cannot tell whether he is a man who dreamed he was a butterfly, or a butterfly now dreaming it is a man. Moral: the line between what is real and what is dreamed is not so fixed as we suppose. — Zhuangzi"
