def "tale:china_mantis_cicada" "A mantis creeps up on a singing cicada, intent on its prey, and never sees the oriole poised to seize the mantis — nor does the oriole see the boy below with his slingshot. Moral: those fixed on the gain before them are blind to the danger behind. — Shuoyuan"
