def "tale:china_qi_sky" "A man of the state of Qi is so tormented by the fear that the sky will fall and the earth give way that he cannot eat or sleep, until a friend reasons him out of his groundless dread. Moral: do not wear yourself out over disasters that will never come. — Liezi"
